# Oracle SQL 치트시트

## 테이블 조회

```sql
SELECT * FROM 테이블명;
```

---

## 특정 컬럼 조회

```sql
SELECT 컬럼1, 컬럼2
FROM 테이블명;
```

---

## 별칭(Alias)

```sql
SELECT EMPNO AS 사번,
       ENAME AS 이름
FROM EMP;
```

---

## 조건 조회

```sql
SELECT *
FROM EMP
WHERE DEPTNO = 10;
```

---

## BETWEEN

```sql
SELECT *
FROM EMP
WHERE SAL BETWEEN 2000 AND 3000;
```

---

## IN

```sql
SELECT *
FROM EMP
WHERE DEPTNO IN (10,20,30);
```

---

## LIKE

```sql
SELECT *
FROM EMP
WHERE ENAME LIKE 'S%';
```

| 기호 | 의미    |
| -- | ----- |
| %  | 0개 이상 |
| _  | 1개 문자 |

---

## 정렬

```sql
SELECT *
FROM EMP
ORDER BY SAL DESC;
```

---

## 그룹 함수

```sql
SELECT
COUNT(*),
SUM(SAL),
AVG(SAL),
MAX(SAL),
MIN(SAL)
FROM EMP;
```

---

## GROUP BY

```sql
SELECT DEPTNO,
       AVG(SAL)
FROM EMP
GROUP BY DEPTNO;
```

---

## HAVING

```sql
SELECT DEPTNO,
       AVG(SAL)
FROM EMP
GROUP BY DEPTNO
HAVING AVG(SAL) >= 3000;
```

---

# JOIN

## INNER JOIN

```sql
SELECT E.ENAME,
       D.DNAME
FROM EMP E
JOIN DEPT D
ON E.DEPTNO = D.DEPTNO;
```

---

## LEFT OUTER JOIN

```sql
SELECT *
FROM EMP E
LEFT JOIN DEPT D
ON E.DEPTNO = D.DEPTNO;
```

---

## SELF JOIN

```sql
SELECT E.ENAME,
       M.ENAME
FROM EMP E
JOIN EMP M
ON E.MGR = M.EMPNO;
```

---

# INSERT

```sql
INSERT INTO MEMBER
VALUES(1,'홍길동');
```

---

# UPDATE

```sql
UPDATE MEMBER
SET NAME='김철수'
WHERE ID=1;
```

---

# DELETE

```sql
DELETE FROM MEMBER
WHERE ID=1;
```

---

# 시퀀스

## 생성

```sql
CREATE SEQUENCE SEQ_MEMBER
START WITH 1
INCREMENT BY 1;
```

## 사용

```sql
SELECT SEQ_MEMBER.NEXTVAL
FROM DUAL;
```

